JP: このツールを使用して、分離された Kubernetes サンドボックス環境で Python、JavaScript、TypeScript のコードを実行します。コード実行、コマンド実行、ファイル操作、セッション管理をサポートします。\n24:       zh_Hans: 使用此工具在隔离的 Kubernetes 沙箱环境中执行 Python、JavaScript 或 TypeScript 代码。支持代码执行、命令执行、文件操作和会话管理。\n25:       pt_BR: Use esta ferramenta para executar código Python, JavaScript ou TypeScript em ambientes sandbox Kubernetes isolados. Suporta execução de código, execução de comandos, operações de arquivo e gerenciamento de sessão.\n26: parameters:\n27:   - name: router_url\n28:     type: string\n29:     required: true\n30:     form: form\n31:     label:\n32:       en_US: Router URL\n33:       ja_JP: ルーター URL\n34:       zh_Hans: 路由器 URL\n35:       pt_BR: URL do Roteador\n36:     human_description:\n37:       en_US: Base URL of the AgentCube router service\n38:       ja_JP: AgentCube ルーターサービスのベース URL\n39:       zh_Hans: AgentCube 路由器服务的基础 URL\n40:       pt_BR: URL base do serviço do roteador AgentCube\n41:     llm_description: The base URL of the AgentCube router service for code execution requests\n42:   - name: workload_manager_url\n43:     type: string\n44:     required: true\n45:     form: form\n46:     label:\n47:       en_US: Workload Manager URL\n48:       ja_JP: ワークロードマネージャー URL\n49:       zh_Hans: 工作负载管理器 URL\n50:       pt_BR: URL do Gerenciador de Carga de Trabalho\n51:     human_description:\n52:       en_US: Base URL of the AgentCube workload manager service\n53:       ja_JP: AgentCube ワークロードマネージャーサービスのベース URL\n54:       zh_Hans: AgentCube 工作负载管理器服务的基础 URL\n55:       pt_BR: URL base do serviço do gerenciador de carga de trabalho AgentCube\n56:     llm_description: The base URL of the AgentCube workload manager service for session creation and management\n57:   - name: language\n58:     type: select\n59:     required: false\n60:     form: llm\n61:     options:\n62:       - value: python\n63:         label: python\n64:       - value: javascript\n65:         label: javascript\n66:       - value: typescript\n67:         label: typescript\n68:     label:\n69:       en_US: Programming Language\n70:       ja_JP: プログラミング言語\n71:       zh_Hans: 编程语言\n72:       pt_BR: Linguagem de Programação\n73:     human_description:\n74:       en_US: \"Programming language for code execution (default: python)\"\n75:       ja_JP: \"コード実行のプログラミング言語 (デフォルト：python)\"\n76:       zh_Hans: \"代码执行的编程语言 (默认：python)\"\n77:       pt_BR: \"Linguagem de programação para execução de código (padrão: python)\"\n78:     llm_description: The programming language to use for code execution. Choose from python, javascript, or typescript\n79:   - name: code\n80:     type: string\n81:     required: false\n82:     form: llm\n83:     label:\n84:       en_US: Code\n85:       ja_JP: コード\n86:       zh_Hans: 代码\n87:       pt_BR: Código\n88:     human_description:\n89:       en_US: Source code to execute in the sandbox\n90:       ja_JP: サンドボックスで実行するソースコード\n91:       zh_Hans: 在沙箱中执行的源代码\n92:       pt_BR: Código-fonte a ser executado na sandbox\n93:     llm_description: The source code to execute in the sandbox environment\n94:   - name: command\n95:     type: string\n96:     required: false\n97:     form: llm\n98:     label:\n99:       en_US: Command\n100:       ja_JP: コマンド\n101:       zh_Hans: 命令\n102:       pt_BR: Comando\n103:     human_description:\n104:       en_US: Shell command to execute in the sandbox\n105:       ja_JP: サンドボックスで実行するシェルコマンド\n106:       zh_Hans: 在沙箱中执行的 Shell 命令\n107:       pt_BR: Comando de shell a ser executado na sandbox\n108:     llm_description: A shell command to execute in the sandbox environment\n109:   - name: session_id\n110:     type: string\n111:     required: false\n112:     form: llm\n113:     label:\n114:       en_US: Session ID\n115:       ja_JP: セッション ID\n116:       zh_Hans: 会话 ID\n117:       pt_BR: ID da Sessão\n118:     human_description:\n119:       en_US: Existing session ID to reuse (optional)\n120:       ja_JP: 再利用する既存のセッション ID（オプション）\n121:       zh_Hans: 要重用的现有会话 ID（可选）\n122:       pt_BR: ID de sessão