{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886459402,"sessionID":"ses_284ebc2e3ffeAIWV4m8xt1M7jl","part":{"id":"prt_d7b14d4d5001GZKsFdPhbPvrLC","messageID":"msg_d7b14c1b7001GEyD98eMtcxE7S","sessionID":"ses_284ebc2e3ffeAIWV4m8xt1M7jl","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_c8e3475e5d764047b86ade72","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube Integrations — Design\n2: \n3: Sources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/integrations/dify-plugin/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/example/pcap-analyzer/`.\n4: \n5: ## Dify plugin — file map\n6: \n7: | File | Role |\n8: |------|------|\n9: | `main.py` | `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()` |\n10: | `manifest.yaml` | Root plugin manifest for Dify |\n11: | `provider/agentcube.yaml` | Tool provider identity + tool list + Python entry |\n12: | `provider/agentcube.py` | `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider` |\n13: | `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml` | Tool parameter schema |\n14: | `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` | `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool` |\n15: | `requirements.txt` | `dify-plugin` + `agentcube-sdk` pins |\n16: | `GUIDE.md`, `README.md`, `PRIVACY.md`, `.difyignore` | Docs / packaging |\n17: \n18: ## `manifest.yaml` structure (exact top-level keys)\n19: \n20: From source:\n21: \n22: - `version`: `0.0.2`\n23: - `type`: `plugin`\n24: - `author`: `volcano-sh`\n25: - `name`: `agentcube`\n26: - `label`: map `en_US`, `ja_JP`, `zh_Hans`, `pt_BR` → `Agentcube`\n27: - `description`: multilingual strings (AgentCube description)\n28: - `icon`: `icon.png`\n29: - `icon_dark`: `icon-dark.png`\n30: - `resource`: `memory`, `permission` subtree (`tool`, `model`, `endpoint`, `app`, `storage` flags and sizes)\n31: - `plugins.tools`: list `[provider/agentcube.yaml]`\n32: - `meta`: `version`, `arch` (`amd64`, `arm64`), `runner` (`language: python`, `version: \"3.12\"`, `entrypoint: main`), `minimum_dify_version: null`\n33: - `created_at`, `privacy`, `repo`, `verified`\n34: \n35: ## `provider/agentcube.yaml` structure\n36: \n37: - `identity`: `author`, `name`, `label` (multilingual), `description` (multilingual), `icon`\n38: - Commented `oauth_schema` block (not active)\n39: - `tools`: list `[tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml]`\n40: - `extra.python.source`: `provider/agentcube.py`\n41: \n42: ## Tool definition (`tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`)\n43: \n44: - `identity.name`: `agentcube-code-interpreter`\n45: - `identity.author`: `agentcube`\n46: - `identity.label` / `description` (human + llm strings)\n47: - `parameters` (each has `name`, `type`, `required`, `label`, `human_description`, `llm_description`, `form`):\n48: \n49: | name | type | required | form | notes |\n50: |------|------|----------|------|-------|\n51: | `router_url` | string | true | form | |\n52: | `workload_manager_url` | string | true | form | |\n53: | `language` | select | false | llm | options: `python`, `javascript`, `typescript` |\n54: | `code` | string | false | llm | |\n55: | `command` | string | false | llm | |\n56: | `session_id` | string | false | llm | |\n57: | `session_reuse` | boolean | false | llm | |\n58: | `code_interpreter_id` | string | false | llm | |\n59: \n60: - `extra.python.source`: `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`\n61: \n62: ## Provider implementation (`provider/agentcube.py`)\n63: \n64: ```python\n65: from dify_plugin import ToolProvider\n66: from dify_plugin.errors.tool import ToolProviderCredentialValidationError\n67: \n68: class AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider):\n69:     def _validate_credentials(self, credentials: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n70:         try:\n71:             \"\"\" IMPLEMENT YOUR VALIDATION HERE \"\"\"\n72:         except Exception as e:\n73:             raise ToolProviderCredentialValidationError(str(e))\n74: ```\n75: \n76: (OAuth helper methods are present only as comments.)\n77: \n78: ## Tool implementation (`tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`)\n79: \n80: ```python\n81: from collections.abc import Generator\n82: from typing import Any\n83: from dify_plugin import Tool\n84: from dify_plugin.entities.tool import ToolInvokeMessage\n85: from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient\n86: \n87: class AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool(Tool):\n88:     def _invoke(self, tool_parameters: dict[str, Any]) -> Generator[ToolInvokeMessage]:\n89:         result = self.execute(**tool_parameters)\n90:         yield self.create_json_message(result)\n91: \n92:     def execute(\n93:         self,\n94:         router_url=None,\n95:         workload_manager_url=None,\n96:         language=\"python\",\n97:         code_interpreter_id=None,\n98:         session_id=None,\n99:         code=None,\n100:         command=None,\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 209. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube Integrations — Design\n\nSources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/integrations/dify-plugin/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/example/pcap-analyzer/`.\n\n## Dify plugin — file map\n\n| File | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `main.py` | `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()` |\n| `manifest.yaml` | Root plugin manifest for Dify |\n| `provider/agentcube.yaml` | Tool provider identity + tool list + Python entry |\n| `provider/agentcube.py` | `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider` |\n| `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml` | Tool parameter schema |\n| `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` | `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool` |\n| `requirements.txt` | `dify-plugin` + `agentcube-sdk` pins |\n| `GUIDE.md`, `README.md`, `PRIVACY.md`, `.difyignore` | Docs / packaging |\n\n## `manifest.yaml` structure (exact top-level keys)\n\nFrom source:","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-